\begin{align}
\pm\int_{\Omega}v\,qg & =\int_{\Omega}v\,\vec{\nabla}\cdot\vec{j}_{u}\\
0 & =\int_{\Omega}v\,\vec{\nabla}\cdot\vec{j}_{u}\mp\int_{\Omega}v\,qg\label{eq:mixed-dd-g}
\end{align}

\end_inset

and we're done.
 Next we rearrange 
