\begin_inset Formula $\int_{\Omega}\vec{\sigma}\cdot\vec{\nabla}a+\int_{\Omega}a(\vec{\nabla}\cdot\vec{\sigma})=\oint_{\Gamma}\vec{\sigma}a\cdot\hat{n}$
\end_inset

